{"tid":2320560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 全球首宗武漢肺炎狗隻傳狗隻","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T06:37:06.000Z","uid":174502,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f7280c5c1e161fe9229e580cc1a7d1a820223b","tid":2320560,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"近日接連有警員染疫，警方公佈再多一名駐守機場警區的男警長初步確診，他是早前確診的3名同樣駐守機場的警員緊密接觸者，他獲安排家居隔離，昨晚（10日）隔離期間感到不適，今日（11日）初步確診，本港9日內已有8名警察染疫，機場警區染疫警亦增至4名。此外，衞生防護中心資料顯示，柴灣已婚警察宿舍2座5日內，再多一名四旬婦確診武漢肺炎，這兩名患者都有機會是警嫂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前確診的駐守機場警區3名染疫男警，分別為41歲警長、32歲警員及28歲警員，日前不適，12月7日求醫，8日晚上初步確診。衞生防護中心在9日的疫情記者會指，其中1人確診，但拒絕透露其確診編號；10日公佈的患者名單顯示，一名在12月6日發病的41歲男子、第7189號個案，住油塘油美苑淑美閣。油美苑是紀律部隊員工宿舍，單位主要分配予警務處，其次為消防處等部隊。第7189號個案可能就是9日確診的41歲男警長。"},{"pid":"cbde0c5237682b68fd29bb68ddb96d669610c639","tid":2320560,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993c944a85014e3ba3c29746c811f4acafdcb8f5","tid":2320560,"uid":212681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"h