<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f2e6a62a9af33314c2910438ee8ff9863b7fde","tid":2320560,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580a0015a8241cbd61648149d2f9682787624cac","tid":2320560,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ffd875003c038d45ae6143fbbc44bb2b4855ec","tid":2320560,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"見到標題嚇親, 狗狗大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩係呢D狗, 攞去非人道毀滅唔該"},{"pid":"701fea5fe1242c9578c2268959f854b018c354b3","tid":2320560,"uid":288393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"}]}